    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy. This beauty is in pristine condition\u2014honestly, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the lot! I've babied this car since day one, keeping it garage-kept and spotless. It drives like an absolute dream and is ready for its next adventure. You won't find one cleaner than this! Feel free to reach out if you want to come take a look!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
