    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, maintained to the highest possible standard. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating, showing no rock chips, swirl marks, or door dings. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine condition; the premium leather seats are supple and unmarked, the dashboard is free of any sun damage, and the original floor mats are spotless. Mechanically, it is flawless, backed by a comprehensive binder of every service record since day one. Always garage-kept and never driven in inclement weather, this car performs exactly as it did the day it left the showroom floor. If you are seeking an investment-grade example that requires absolutely zero reconditioning, this is the one.",
      "price": 44900.0,
